(211, '<h4>\n	Instruments dels cinc continents:</h4>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;- <b>Oceania</b>: didgerid&uacute; australi&agrave;, brunzidor, cargol de mar, sonallers...</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;- <b>&Agrave;sia</b>:</p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp; d&#39;India: sitar, bansuri, hectara,&nbsp;...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - d&#39;Orient Mitj&agrave;: llaut &agrave;rab, ney i qavala &agrave;rabs, derbukha, riq, baglama i cumbus turcs, magrouna egipci, sipsi turc, argul egipci...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - de la Xina: guanzi, dizi, hulusi, bawu, ...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - De Nepal, Tibet, Vietnam i altres: campanes, bols, tambor de m&agrave;, gong, dan moi (arpa de boca),&nbsp;... </span></p>\n<p>\n	- <b>Europa</b>:</p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Mediterranis: bouzouki grec, mandolina, launedas sard, castanyoles (del magreb, de les balears, ...), cr&ograve;tals, bendir,&nbsp;...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Centreeuropeus: fujara eslovaca -la flauta m&eacute;s gran del m&oacute;n-, low wistle&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; celta, qaval dels Balcans, dvinitsa d&#39;Ucraina... </span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Catalans i ib&egrave;rics: gralla, guitarra, pandereta, pandero quadrat, xeremies de les Balears i Pitiuses... </span></p>\n<p>\n	<b>-&Agrave;frica: </b></p>\n<p>\n	-<span burkina="" fasso:="" new="" span="" times="">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Magreb: gembri, qarbabs, zummara, taarija...</span></p>\n<p>\n	- <b>Am&egrave;rica</b>:</p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - de Brasil: berimbau, cuica, agogos, xiulet de nas i xiulet de samba,&nbsp;&nbsp; octobloc, surdo, ...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&