(211, '<p>\n	Es tracta d&#39;una audici&oacute; d&#39;instruments musicals de tot tipus (vent, corda i percussi&oacute;) dels 5 continents: veurem des d&#39;instruments d&#39;Oceania fins a instruments asi&agrave;tics (xinesos, hind&uacute;s, tibetans, vietnamites, ...), passant per instruments europeus (mediterranis, de centreeuropa, de pa&iuml;sos n&ograve;rdics, de Catalunya...) fins als africans i americans.</p>\n<p>\n	Coneixerem en viu alguns dels instruments m&eacute;s representatius, bonics i especials dels cinc continents i com aquests s&rsquo;han transformat i adaptat seguint els moviments migratoris dels humans, veurem com la m&uacute;sica ens conecta a tots dins una gran sonosfera :</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;- <b>Oceania</b>: didgerid&uacute; australi&agrave;, brunzidor, cargol de mar, sonallers...</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;- <b>&Agrave;sia</b>:</p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp; d&#39;India: sitar, bansuri, hectara,&nbsp;...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - d&#39;Orient Mitj&agrave;: llaut &agrave;rab, ney i qavala &agrave;rabs, derbukha, riq, baglama i cumbus turcs, magrouna egipci, sipsi turc, argul egipci...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - de la Xina: guanzi, dizi, hulusi, bawu, ...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - De Nepal, Tibet, Vietnam i altres: campanes, bols, tambor de m&agrave;, gong, dan moi (arpa de boca),&nbsp;... </span></p>\n<p>\n	- <b>Europa</b>:</p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Mediterranis: bouzouki grec, mandolina, launedas sard, castanyoles (del magreb, de les balears, ...), cr&ograve;tals, bendir,&nbsp;...</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Centreeuropeus: fujara eslovaca -la flauta m&eacute;s gran del m&oacute;n-, low wistle&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; celta, qaval dels Balcans, dvinitsa d&#39;