(259, '<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	A partir de la tercera setmana de Setembre</p>\n<h4>\n	TALLER D&#39;INSTRUMENTS I M&Uacute;SIQUES TRADICIONALS I D&#39;ARREU.</h4>\n<p align="LEFT">\n	Us oferirem classes individuals o en grup d&rsquo;istruments tradicionals de diferents cultures:</p>\n<p align="LEFT">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	- CORDES: <strong>llaut aragon&egrave;s, llaut &agrave;rab, baglama turc, &ccedil;umbus, sitar hind&uacute;, bouzouki, viola d&#39;amor i dilruba.</strong></p>\n<p>\n	- PERCUSSIONS: <strong>tables hind&uacute;s, derbukha, riqq, bendir, caj&oacute;n flamenco, percussi&oacute; llatina, percussi&oacute; africana</strong>, etc.</p>\n<p>\n	- VENTS: <strong>ney i qawala &agrave;rab, didgeridoo, bansuri, flautes de bec,</strong> etc.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	Professors:</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	En <strong>Dani Ib&aacute;&ntilde;ez</strong>&nbsp; a les cordes.</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	En<strong> Jaume Cat&agrave;</strong>, la <strong>Nuri Mad&iacute;</strong> i l&rsquo;<strong>Aniol L&oacute;pez</strong> a les percussions.</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	La <strong>M&iacute;riam Encinas</strong> i en <strong>Jordi Par&eacute;s</strong> als vents.</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	A m&eacute;s a m&eacute;s de classes i sessions regulars, tamb&eacute; portarem a terme master-class, cursos monogr&agrave;fics i intensius, com per exemple: Curs de cante amb Alba Guerrero, Curs de ney i qavala &agrave;rabs amb Mohamed Fetyan, Introducci&oacute; als Maqqams &agrave;rabs, etc.</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p align="JUSTIFY">\n	Properament us farem arribar m&eacute;s informaci&oacute;.</p>\n', 'ca'),
